{"id": 6022, "title": "Ticket #6022: Add CumulativeRemoteUserCpu and ...SysCpu attributes to jobs", "description": "<blockquote>\nHTCondor records <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=RemoteSysCpu\" title=\"Remote Sys Cpu\">RemoteSysCpu</a></span> and <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=RemoteUserCpu\" title=\"Remote User Cpu\">RemoteUserCpu</a></span> time for each job, but it only measures each execution attempt.  We should add <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=CumulativeRemoteUserCpu\" title=\"Cumulative Remote User Cpu\">CumulativeRemoteUserCpu</a></span> and <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=CumulativeRemoteSysCpu\" title=\"Cumulative Remote Sys Cpu\">CumulativeRemoteSysCpu</a></span> to sum up cpu time over multiple preemptions and other execution attempts.</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2017-Jan-17 15:41</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/5e2bfa52a24323cd23d663d2fa4d615dec69a919\">[50000]</a></span>: Documnet <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"defer\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=6022\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('6022'); return false;\" title=\"Add CumulativeRemoteUserCpu and ...SysCpu attributes to jobs\">#6022</a></span>  (By Greg Thain )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2016-Nov-28 09:58</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/com